<content>1 XWiki Syntax

XWiki allows you to create internet pages without using HTML thanks to the Wiki Syntax. This Wiki Syntax is a simple way to modify the aspect of a document as well as create links between documents.


This document briefly explains the wiki syntax. 

{pre}
&lt;table class="wiki-table" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="80%"&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th width="25%"&gt;Description:&lt;/th&gt;
