&lt;td&gt;

&lt;b class="bold"&gt;Bold&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
There are two ways to mark text as bold.
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;

Here is some text with a *bold* word.
Here is some text with an __underlined__ word.

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
Here is some text with a &lt;strong class="strong"&gt;bold&lt;/strong&gt; word.
Here is some text with a &lt;b class="bold"&gt;bold&lt;/b&gt; word.

&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;b class="bold"&gt;Italics&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;

~~Here is some text in italics~~

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;i class="italic"&gt;Here is some text in italics&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;b class="bold"&gt;Striked Text&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;

--Here is some striked text--

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;strike class="strike"&gt;Here is some striked text&lt;/strike&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;

&lt;b class="bold"&gt;Wiki Links&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p class="paragraph"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;

Wiki Links:

* [WebHome]
* [Web Home]
* [web home&gt;WebHome]
* [Main.WebHome]
* [web home|Main.WebHome]

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
Wiki Links:
